                  <summary>I) Homily by Theodotus of Ancyra on the commemoration of St George, for
                     the 23th of Miyāzyā (fols. 4ra-15rb) &#xD; - Introduction (fols. 4ra-7rb, l.21)
                     &#xD; - Discourse on the origin of the genealogy of St George (fols. 7rb,
                     l.21-15rb, l.3) &#xD; II) Gadla Giyorgis “Vita of George” (fols. 15rb,
                     l.3-93rb, l.6) &#xD; III) Taʾammǝra Giyorgis “Miracles of George”: 12 miracles
                     (fols. 93ra, l.7-108va) &#xD; - Introduction (fols. 93ra, l.6-96va, l.14)&#xD;
                     &#xD; Additio 1.</summary>
